{"type":null,"faqId":43598,"title":"手机不停重启，长按电源键也没用，怎么处理？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{color:black;}\n.s2{color:blue;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:center;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:12pt;}\n.p3{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1. 确保手机处于有电状态。给手机充电时，充电指示灯会闪烁，保持充电状态等待一段时间再尝试开机操作。（如果手机还可以备份信息记得马上备份，建议平时重要信息，要有SD或者其他方式备份）。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">2. 手机卡死无反应的情况下，可以长按电源键10s强制重启。看看是否可以恢复。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">3. 到EMUI官方网站下载对应手机版本的rom完整包，一定要找对版本，不然刷进去更麻烦。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">4. 把下载好的完整包解压缩，得到一个dload文件夹，把文件夹用读卡器存到SD卡里，整个存进去，存到sd卡根目录里。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">5. 关闭手机，然后同时按住音量加+音量减+电源键，手机会进行强制重刷固件的操作，完成后会自动开机。可以参考：</span><a href=\"http://jingyan.baidu.com/article/cdddd41c80395f53cb00e12e.html\"><span class=\"s2\">http://jingyan.baidu.com/article/cdddd41c80395f53cb00e12e.html</span></a>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">或者关闭手机，手机通过USB线与电脑连接，然后同时长按你的电源（又称power键）和音量上键（就是把声音调大的那个了）10s，大概一两分钟后进入erecovery界面，可以通过连接WLAN后下载软件包升级。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=152464\" style=\"width:2.6861112in;height:3.1631944in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span>* 图示仅供参考，具体操作请以手机实际界面为准。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":144,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"9099","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442399196000,"seriesProductName":"CRR-CL10,CRR-TL10","visitedTimes":149,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"黑屏,重启","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}